{"word":"G4880 - συναποθνήσκω - synapothnḗskō - soon-ap-oth-nace'-ko - Be dead with","slug":"G4880","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναποθνήσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>synapothnḗskō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-ap-oth-nace'-ko"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be dead with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B8;&#x03BD;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03C9; - sunapothne&#x0304;sko&#x0304;</b> - <i>soon-ap-oth-nace'-ko</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G599\">G599</a>; to <i>decease</i> (literally) in company <i>with</i>, or (figuratively) similarly <i>to:</i> - be dead (die) with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957\">G4957</a>"}]}